    "schedule_read": "D512 score-page-only rocWMMA source-boundary rung. One CTA owns a token/selected tile, computes QK and dO.V score pages with rocWMMA from gathered selected KV, forms prob/scaled-dP in shared memory, then sinks a checksum without contribution sweep or dKV writes. The score producer reuses each selected-KV D16 tile across all four H16 head blocks before advancing D. A four-wave CTA variant maps one wavefront to each H16 head block during score-page production, then maps wavefronts to consecutive D16 contribution consumers so the score page is consumed inside the same workgroup."
  },
  "contract": {
    "formula": "dKV[g,d] += sum_{token,k,h:group(token,k)=g} prob[token,h,k] * grad_output[token,h,d] + scaled_dP[token,h,k] * q[token,h,d]",
